    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813000/extras/ed3cc600302d21f1ef6f080be0989629.avif?t=1769271054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813000/extras_big/ed3cc600302d21f1ef6f080be0989629.avif?t=1769271054 width=800 height=320 /></span>SoulSide is a JRPG that blends traditional mechanics with new ideas, packaged in detailed pixel art graphics. A mix of familiar gameplay and fresh ideas to keep things interesting.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JUMPING and ELEVATION</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TURN-BASED combat with MINIGAMES for attacking and dodging</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >on-screen enemy encounters (NO RANDOM battles)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a large cast of characters and funny dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >lots of hidden PUZZLES and SECRETS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A CONCERNING AMOUNT OF MUSHROOMS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SoulSide combines lots of  elements to create a JRPG thats feels as unique as possible.</p>",
